{
  "texts": [
    "While the median of the difference between the two scores is 34, for bilingual LeoLM it is 264.",
    "Excluding the new factual and bias-related questions and therefore making results better comparable to the older English ones, the performance of the best 7b model in German was only 43.2% compared to 62.2% in English.",
    "We conclude that there is significant room for improvement for these German models.",
    "We hypothesize that there are not yet as high quality German instruction tuning and DPO-datasets as there are in English language.Instruction tuning however, also seems to have its limitations.",
    "Although it can significantly enhance the performance of base models, it still seems to plateau with a given base model."
  ]
}